Interface INonViralNameCacheStrategy<T extends NonViralName>

Type Parameters:

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface INonViralNameCacheStrategy<T extends NonViralName>
extends INameCacheStrategy<T>

A name cache rendering strategy for all TaxonNameBase subclasses. Different TaxonNameBase subclasses could have different strategies.
